Name: Call of Fries
About the game: Call of Fries is a comical fries simulator. Fun physical arcade with drawn graphics and excellent music. No blood - only ketchup! Every potato dreams of getting in your mouth! But it's not that easy. There are always a lot of obstacles on the way. Try to overcome all the traps and fill your stomach! Here are some game features: intuitive mouse control, no blood, just ketchup and mushrooms, complex physical puzzles, great music, many interesting situations. It is highly recommended that you do not play on an empty stomach!
